Package org.apache.tools.ant.taskdefs.optional.ccm

Class Summary
CCMCheck Class common to all check commands (checkout, checkin,checkin default task);
CCMCheckin Task to perform Checkin command to Continuus
CCMCheckinDefault Task to perform Checkin Default task command to Continuus
CCMCheckout Task to perform Checkout command to Continuus
CCMCreateTask Task allows to create new ccm task and set it as the default
CCMReconfigure Task allows to reconfigure a project, recurcively or not
Continuus A base class for creating tasks for executing commands on Continuus 5.1
